SELECT spock.delta_apply('slabel1', 'z'); -- ERROR
ERROR:  column z does not exist in the table slabel1
SELECT spock.delta_apply('slabel1', 'x'); -- repeating call do nothing
INFO:  DDL statement replicated.
 delta_apply 
-------------
